Package sketchy.bytecode

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FieldAnalyzer
    Find, save and update all the available fields given an object or class.
    LocalVariableTableClassVisitor
    ClassVisitor to read local variable table from bytecode and to know which local variables we have in every method body.
    LocalVariableTableMethodVisitor
    MethodVisitor to read local variable table from bytecode and to know which local variables we have in every method body.
    SaveLocalVarValuesClassVisitor
    ClassVisitor to insert instructions to save values of local variables right before each eval().
    SaveLocalVarValuesMethodVisitor
    MethodVisitor to insert instructions to save values of local variables right before each eval().
    StaticFieldAnalyzer  
    StaticGenClassVisitor
    Class visitor for static generation.
    StaticGenMethodVisitor
    MethodVisitor to get available local variables at every eval() method.
    Symbol
    A field or local variable, wrapping name and type together.
    Var
    Class to represent a local variable, which has name, descriptor, local variable index, start bytecode offset and end bytecode offset.
    VariableAnalyzer
    Util class to transform bytecode (to get local variables) and to get fields.
